sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Consumidor as Consumidore/Aplicación
    participant API as API Consulta Cuentas Ahorro <br> Epica 880: ConsultaActivosCliente <br> HU 3933:  GET - /loans-and-deposits/savings-account-retrieves/v1/{customerIdentification}/assets-retrieve
    participant Lib as Librería Pipeline (ConfigMap)
    participant T24 as Wrapper T24 <br> Operación: ConsultaCuentaAhorroxCliente
    participant VAL as Librería Valida Funcionalidad Usuario <br> Epica 59: Componentes transversales <br> HU 17488
    participant Errors as Control de Errores <br> <<Librería de mapeo de errores>>

    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - Consulta Cuentas Ahorros 

    Consumidor->>API: REST Request
    Note right of Consumidor: Header, queryParam: customerReference

    API->>API: Validar Request
    Note over API: Valida campos obligatorios según contrato OpenAPI <br> customerReference (obligatorio)

    API->>API: Validación exitosa

    API->>API: Validar Servicio Regional
    Note over API: domain: SAVINGS_ACCOUNT_RETRIEVES <br> name: CONFIG
    
    API->>API: Validación Regional Exitosa
    Note over API: Servicio habilitado para HN01

    API->>Lib: Consulta Constantes
   
    Lib->>API: Retorna constantes necesarias
    Note left of Lib: columnName = "CUSTOMER" <br> operand = "EQ"

    API->>API: Construye Request Wrapper T24
    Note over API: Mapeo: <br> columnName = cons.columnName <br> criteriaValue = request.customerReference <br> operand = cons.operand

    API->>T24: Consume Wrapper T24 OP: ConsultaCuentaAhorroxCliente
    Note right of API: columnName, criteriaValue, operand

    T24->>API: Response Wrapper T24
    Note left of T24: ALTACCTID, ACCOUNTNUMBER, ACCOUNTTITLE, <br> CURRENCY,  TOTALBALANCE, RESERVEBALANCE <br> LIENBALANCE, BLOCKEDFUNDSPOS, <br> BLOCKEDFUNDSATM, AVAILABLEBAL, OPERATIONTYPE

    API->>API: Evalua Response Wrapper T24

    alt if (upper-case($successIndicator) = 'SUCCESS' and count($registros) = 0)

        API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

        Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

        API->> Consumidor: REST Response Error
        Note left of API: HTTP 404: No Records Found

    else if (upper-case($successIndicator) = 'SUCCESS' and count($registros) > 0)

        API->>API: Construye Response campo visaFloatingBalance
        Note over API:If (BLOCKEDFUNDSPOS = "NaN" and BLOCKEDFUNDSATM = "NaN") then visaFloatingBalance = "0.00" <br> else If (BLOCKEDFUNDSPOS != "NaN" and BLOCKEDFUNDSATM != "NaN") then visaFloatingBalance = BLOCKEDFUNDSPOS + BLOCKEDFUNDSATM <br> else If (BLOCKEDFUNDSPOS = "NaN") then visaFloatingBalance =  BLOCKEDFUNDSATM <br> else visaFloatingBalance = BLOCKEDFUNDSPOS 

        API->>API: Construye Response API
        Note over API: assetType = "AHO" <br> If (ALTACCTID exist) then assetProductNumber = ALTACCTID else assetProductNumber = ACCOUNTNUMBER <br> assetProductName = ACCOUNTTITLE <br> assetCurrency = CURRENCY <br> assetTotalBalance = TOTALBALANCE <br> assetReservedBalance = RESERVEBALANCE <br> assetBlockedBalance = LIENBALANCE <br> availableBalance = AVAILABLEBAL <br> productType  = OPERATIONTYPE <br> openingDate = OPENINGDATE (Format: YYYY-MM-DD) <br> If INACTIVEMARKER != "Y" then productStatus = "ACTIVE" <br> else productStatus = "INACTIVE"

        API->>VAL: Uso Librería Validación de Funcionalidad Usuario
        Note right of API: Campos: <br> req = requestAPI, <br> target { type = "API", id = "savings-account-retrieves", method = "assets-retrieve" }, <br> data = responseAPI

        VAL->>API: Response Librería Validación Funcionalidad Usuario
        Note left of VAL: Retrona Campos Filtrados

        API->>Consumidor: REST Response Successful
        Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body
        
    end

    activate API
    alt Exception occurs
        note over Errors: Error Library Handler
        activate Errors
            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error
            Errors -->> API: Retorna código mapeado
        deactivate Errors
        activate Consumidor
            API-->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        deactivate Consumidor
        Note over Consumidor,Errors: Diagrama guía de manejo de errores <br> http://bit.ly/4rpKVIU
    end
    deactivate API